{"tid":1271940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果爆塊玻璃，就會民意逆轉既話，咁其實香港人根本唔洗驚","createTime":"2019-07-01T08:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T11:28:09.000Z","uid":251119,"like":920,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"48ceaaf3d50283bcf5e974b8493100c856771bce","tid":1271940,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為佢地根本唔係支持緊你既</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">理念同信念</span></span><br />\n對住一班根本唔係支持你既人<br />\n呢啲所謂既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民意</span></span> 已經唔再值得我地去爭取<br />\n依家成個運動根本上已經比呢啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">假民意</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勒索左</span></span><br />\n真正為左香港好而去抗爭既人<br />\n唔再需要咩住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民意</span></span>呢個包袱<br />\n冇左呢個包袱 話唔定成個運動會更加有效<br />\n而唔似得69至到今日咁<br />\n做左咁多日 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一樣訴求都冇回應</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVr6o8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVr6o8E.png&h=cb94ad7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7KLEG0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7KLEG0.png&h=37a3af2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43c5ccccff3098c8329734c62f68cfb1d708a94b","tid":1271940,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"e91c06a9b697fe7e8d9d705f1f208c5fd64bfbba","tid":1271940,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:20:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e2f5a39863ccb707473ab8398cb41aad250461aa","tid":1271940,"uid":137371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0e5a49245dcbee911820302cf63e36a56e181f49","tid":1271